oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriters Session - Corey Crowder, Liz Rose and Phil Barton - 2016-11-05
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performances by songwriters Corey Crowder, Liz Rose and Phil Barton from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on November 5, 2016.
